Realtek RTL8761BU Bluetooth firmware blobs
==========================================

Files:
  rtl8761bu_fw.bin       — patch firmware (42088 bytes)
  rtl8761bu_config.bin   — patch configuration (6 bytes)

These are uploaded to the dongle by skywatch/remoteid/ble_hci.py at start time.
The chip cannot operate without them, and Windows's generic Bluetooth USB driver
does not ship a copy.

Source
------
Mirrored from https://github.com/andrew-ld/rtl8761b-firmware (master branch),
which is in turn a copy of the rtl_bt/ directory in the upstream linux-firmware
repository at https://git.kernel.org/pub/scm/linux/kernel/git/firmware/linux-firmware.git

